pull_request.title: Enable building on platforms without _Atomic support
pull_request.body:
Preparation for native win32 build.
Also raise release ID.

pull_request.title: Standalone ctest
pull_request.body:
This eliminates the `ctest` dependency on `scripts/runtests.sh` in preparation for a shellscript-free test suite (for MSVC-based CI). 

Also contains a workaround for known OpenSSL issues (https://github.com/openssl/openssl/issues/20981 https://github.com/openssl/openssl/issues/21023).
